        <ul>
            <li>Cancellation and Re-scheduling:</li>
            <ol>
                <li>Full refund applies only when the cancellation is confirmed seven(7) days before departure day.</li>
                <li>HKD200.00 administrative fee applies for all cancellation and re-scheduling within seven(7) days before departure day.</li>
                <li>On the day of departure, no re-fund for all cancellation; HKD200.00 administrative fee applies to re-scheduling.</li>
